---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="FitQuest – Fitness RPG | Hakan Efe" description="FitQuest: Fitness'ı oyuna dönüştüren React Native mobil uygulaması. XP sistemi, AI koç, haftalık boss, Apple Health entegrasyonu ve daha fazlası.">

<div class="fq-page">

  <header class="fq-header">
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Portföye Dön</a>
    <div class="fq-hero">
      <div class="fq-hero-text">
        <span class="fq-badge">📱 Mobil Uygulama</span>
        <h1><img src="/fitquest/icon.png" alt="FitQuest" class="fq-app-icon" /> FitQuest</h1>
        <p class="fq-tagline">Fitness'ı RPG'ye Dönüştür</p>
        <p class="fq-desc">Antrenman yaptıkça XP kazan, level atla, haftalık bossu yen. AI koç, Apple Health entegrasyonu ve sosyal özelliklerle fitness artık bir oyun.</p>
        <div class="fq-actions">
          <span class="fq-status">🚧 Geliştirme Aşamasında</span>
          <div class="fq-chips">
            <span>React Native</span>
            <span>Expo</span>
            <span>Zustand</span>
            <span>Apple Health</span>
            <span>AI Coach</span>
            <span>PWA</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fq-phone-wrap">
        <div class="fq-phone">
          <div class="fq-phone-notch"></div>
          <div class="fq-phone-screen">
            <div class="fq-screen-header">
              <div>
                <div class="fq-screen-lvl">⚔️ Level 12</div>
                <div class="fq-screen-name">Kahraman Hakan</div>
              </div>
              <div class="fq-screen-xp-wrap">
                <div class="fq-screen-xp-bar"><div class="fq-screen-xp-fill"></div></div>
                <div class="fq-screen-xp-txt">2.400 / 3.000 XP</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fq-screen-stats">
              <div class="fq-stat-chip green">💪 78<span>GÜÇ</span></div>
              <div class="fq-stat-chip blue">❤️ 85<span>DAYANIKLILIK</span></div>
              <div class="fq-stat-chip gold">⚡ 71<span>HIZ</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="fq-boss-card">
              <div class="fq-boss-top">
                <span class="fq-boss-icon">🐉</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="fq-boss-lbl">Haftalık Boss</div>
                  <div class="fq-boss-name">Ejderha Demir</div>
                </div>
                <div class="fq-boss-xp">+500 XP</div>
              </div>
              <div class="fq-boss-bar"><div class="fq-boss-fill"></div></div>
              <div class="fq-boss-txt">3/5 antrenman — %60 hasar verildi</div>
            </div>
            <div class="fq-quest-row">
              <span>🏃 Bugün 30 dk koş</span>
              <span class="fq-quest-done">✓</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fq-quest-row">
              <span>🏋️ Üst vücut antrenmanı</span>
              <span class="fq-quest-pend">●</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-phone-glow"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="fq-main">

    <!-- ÖZELLİKLER -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Özellikler</h2>
      <div class="fq-features">

        <div class="fq-feature-big">
          <span class="fq-fi">⚔️</span>
          <h3>RPG Karakter Sistemi</h3>
          <p>Her antrenman seni güçlendirir. Güç, dayanıklılık ve hız istatistiklerin antrenman türüne göre artar. Level atladıkça yeni özellikler açılır.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fq-feature-big">
          <span class="fq-fi">🐉</span>
          <h3>Haftalık Boss Savaşı</h3>
          <p>Her hafta seni bekleyen bir boss var. Antrenman yaptıkça boss'a hasar verirsin. Haftayı tamamla, büyük XP ödülü kazan.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fq-feature-big ai-feature">
          <div class="fq-ai-label">🤖 AI</div>
          <span class="fq-fi">🧠</span>
          <h3>AI Koç</h3>
          <p>Hedeflerine ve seviyene göre kişiselleştirilmiş haftalık program. AI antrenmanlarını analiz eder, seni dinler ve tavsiyelerde bulunur.</p>
          <img src="/fitquest/ai_robot.png" alt="AI Coach" class="fq-ai-img" />
        </div>

        <div class="fq-feature-sm">
          <span>🍎</span>
          <h3>Apple Health & Watch</h3>
          <p>Adım sayısı, kalori ve antrenman verilerini Apple Health ile senkronize et. Apple Watch desteği.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fq-feature-sm">
          <span>🏆</span>
          <h3>Rozetler & Battle Pass</h3>
          <p>50+ rozet, sezonluk battle pass sistemi ve liderlik tablosuyla rekabet et.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fq-feature-sm">
          <span>🍽️</span>
          <h3>Beslenme Takibi</h3>
          <p>Kalori ve makro takibi, su içme hatırlatıcıları, günlük beslenme hedefleri.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fq-feature-sm">
          <span>📚</span>
          <h3>Egzersiz Kütüphanesi</h3>
          <p>Yüzlerce egzersiz, video rehberler, ev ve spor salonu programları.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fq-feature-sm">
          <span>👥</span>
          <h3>Sosyal & Liderlik</h3>
          <p>Arkadaşlarınla yarış, birlikte quest tamamla, aylık şampiyon ol.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fq-feature-sm">
          <span>📊</span>
          <h3>Vücut Ölçümleri</h3>
          <p>Haftalık ölçüm takibi, grafik analizler ve ilerleme fotoğrafları.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EKRANLAR -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Uygulama Ekranları</h2>
      <div class="fq-screens-grid">
        <div class="fq-mock-screen">
          <div class="fq-mock-top">🏠 Ana Sayfa</div>
          <div class="fq-mock-body">
            <div class="fq-mock-card purple">⚔️ Level 12 · 2400 XP</div>
            <div class="fq-mock-card dark">🐉 Haftalık Boss — %60</div>
            <div class="fq-mock-card dark">🎯 Günlük Görevler</div>
            <div class="fq-mock-row"><span>🏃 Koşu</span><span class="done">✓</span></div>
            <div class="fq-mock-row"><span>🏋️ Spor Salonu</span><span class="pend">○</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-mock-screen">
          <div class="fq-mock-top">🧠 AI Koç</div>
          <div class="fq-mock-body">
            <img src="/fitquest/ai_robot.png" alt="AI" class="fq-mock-ai" />
            <div class="fq-mock-bubble">"Bu hafta üst vücut odaklı çalışalım. 3 gün antrenman öneriyorum."</div>
            <div class="fq-mock-card purple">📋 Haftalık Program Oluştur</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-mock-screen">
          <div class="fq-mock-top">🏋️ Antrenman</div>
          <div class="fq-mock-body">
            <div class="fq-mock-card green">⏱️ 00:24:37</div>
            <div class="fq-mock-ex-row"><span>Bench Press</span><span>80kg · 4×8</span></div>
            <div class="fq-mock-ex-row"><span>Squat</span><span>100kg · 3×6</span></div>
            <div class="fq-mock-ex-row"><span>Pull-up</span><span>BW · 3×10</span></div>
            <div class="fq-mock-card purple">+320 XP kazanıldı</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-mock-screen">
          <div class="fq-mock-top">🏆 Rozetler</div>
          <div class="fq-mock-body">
            <div class="fq-badges">
              <div class="fq-badge-item unlocked">🔥<span>7 Gün</span></div>
              <div class="fq-badge-item unlocked">💪<span>İlk 50</span></div>
              <div class="fq-badge-item unlocked">🏃<span>Koşucu</span></div>
              <div class="fq-badge-item locked">🏅<span>Efsane</span></div>
              <div class="fq-badge-item locked">⚡<span>Flash</span></div>
              <div class="fq-badge-item locked">🐉<span>Boss</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TEKNİK -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Teknik Detaylar</h2>
      <div class="fq-tech-grid">
        <div class="fq-tech-item">
          <span>⚛️</span>
          <div>
            <strong>React Native + Expo</strong>
            <p>iOS ve Android için tek kod tabanı, Expo SDK ile hızlı geliştirme</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-tech-item">
          <span>🐻</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Zustand</strong>
            <p>Global state yönetimi — karakter, antrenman, beslenme ve sosyal veriler</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-tech-item">
          <span>🍎</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Apple Health & Watch</strong>
            <p>HealthKit entegrasyonu, Apple Watch bağlantısı, arka planda veri senkronizasyonu</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-tech-item">
          <span>🤖</span>
          <div>
            <strong>AI Koç Sistemi</strong>
            <p>Kişiselleştirilmiş program oluşturma, antrenman analizi ve akıllı öneriler</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-tech-item">
          <span>🔔</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Push Notifications</strong>
            <p>Expo Notifications ile antrenman hatırlatıcıları ve boss uyarıları</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fq-tech-item">
          <span>📱</span>
          <div>
            <strong>PWA Desteği</strong>
            <p>Web üzerinden de erişilebilir, Progressive Web App olarak ana ekrana eklenebilir</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer class="fq-footer">
    <p>Hakan Efe · <a href="mailto:hakanefe1141@gmail.com">hakanefe1141@gmail.com</a> · <a href="/">hakanefe.com</a></p>
  </footer>

</div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .fq-page { min-height: 100vh; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: "Inter", sans-serif; }

  /* HEADER */
  .fq-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0f 0%, #0f0a1a 40%, #0a150f 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a3e;
    padding: 28px 40px 48px;
  }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
    color: #a78bfa; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500;
    padding: 7px 14px; border: 1px solid #2a2a3e; border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 32px; transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { border-color: #7c3aed; opacity: 1; }

  .fq-hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }

  .fq-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(76,175,80,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(76,175,80,0.35);
    color: #86efac; border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 4px 14px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .fq-hero-text h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; color: white;
    margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
  }
  .fq-app-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(108,99,255,0.4); }

  .fq-tagline {
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6C63FF, #FF6584);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .fq-desc { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 28px; }

  .fq-actions { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .fq-status {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(251,191,36,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.3);
    color: #fbbf24; border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .fq-chips { display: flex; gap: 7px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .fq-chips span {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 4px 12px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
  }

  /* PHONE MOCKUP */
  .fq-phone-wrap { position: relative; }
  .fq-phone {
    width: 240px; background: #0F0F1A;
    border: 2px solid #2a2a3e; border-radius: 36px;
    padding: 20px 14px; position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(108,99,255,0.25), 0 0 0 6px #1a1a2e;
  }
  .fq-phone-notch {
    width: 70px; height: 10px; background: #0a0a0f;
    border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; margin: 0 auto 14px;
  }
  .fq-phone-screen { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .fq-screen-header { margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .fq-screen-lvl { color: #6C63FF; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; }
  .fq-screen-name { color: white; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .fq-screen-xp-bar { height: 5px; background: #2a2a3e; border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .fq-screen-xp-fill { height: 100%; width: 80%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6C63FF, #FF6584); border-radius: 3px; }
  .fq-screen-xp-txt { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.6rem; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; }

  .fq-screen-stats { display: flex; gap: 5px; margin: 4px 0; }
  .fq-stat-chip {
    flex: 1; background: #1a1a2e; border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 6px 4px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px;
  }
  .fq-stat-chip.green { color: #4CAF50; }
  .fq-stat-chip.blue { color: #60a5fa; }
  .fq-stat-chip.gold { color: #FFD700; }
  .fq-stat-chip span { font-size: 0.48rem; color: #64748b; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; }

  .fq-boss-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D1B4E, #1a1a2e); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px; }
  .fq-boss-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; margin-bottom: 7px; }
  .fq-boss-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .fq-boss-lbl { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.55rem; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; }
  .fq-boss-name { color: white; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .fq-boss-xp { background: rgba(255,215,0,0.15); color: #FFD700; border-radius: 5px; padding: 2px 6px; font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: auto; }
  .fq-boss-bar { height: 4px; background: #2a2a3e; border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .fq-boss-fill { height: 100%; width: 60%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #FF6584); }
  .fq-boss-txt { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.55rem; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; }

  .fq-quest-row {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    background: #1a1a2e; border-radius: 7px; padding: 6px 9px;
    font-size: 0.65rem; color: #e2e8f0;
  }
  .fq-quest-done { color: #4CAF50; font-weight: 700; }
  .fq-quest-pend { color: #64748b; }

  .fq-phone-glow {
    position: absolute; bottom: -20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 160px; height: 40px;
    background: rgba(108,99,255,0.35); filter: blur(20px);
    border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* MAIN */
  .fq-main { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 24px 60px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 64px; }

  .section-title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .section-title::after { content: ""; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

  /* FEATURES */
  .fq-features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .fq-feature-big {
    grid-column: span 1;
    background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .fq-feature-big:hover { border-color: #6C63FF; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .fq-fi { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .fq-feature-big h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .fq-feature-big p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }

  .ai-feature { border-color: rgba(108,99,255,0.3); background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card), rgba(108,99,255,0.05)); }
  .fq-ai-label {
    position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 16px;
    background: rgba(108,99,255,0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,0.4);
    color: #a78bfa; border-radius: 100px; padding: 2px 10px;
    font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .fq-ai-img {
    position: absolute; bottom: -10px; right: -10px;
    width: 90px; opacity: 0.25; pointer-events: none;
  }

  .fq-feature-sm {
    background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .fq-feature-sm:hover { border-color: #6C63FF; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .fq-feature-sm > span { font-size: 1.5rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .fq-feature-sm h3 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .fq-feature-sm p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

  /* SCREENS GRID */
  .fq-screens-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
  .fq-mock-screen {
    background: #0F0F1A; border: 1px solid #2a2a3e;
    border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .fq-mock-top {
    background: #1a1a2e; padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a3e;
  }
  .fq-mock-body { padding: 12px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 7px; }
  .fq-mock-card {
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 10px;
    font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; color: white;
  }
  .fq-mock-card.purple { background: rgba(108,99,255,0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,0.3); color: #a78bfa; }
  .fq-mock-card.dark { background: #1a1a2e; border: 1px solid #2a2a3e; color: #94a3b8; }
  .fq-mock-card.green { background: rgba(76,175,80,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(76,175,80,0.3); color: #86efac; text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; }
  .fq-mock-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 0.68rem; color: #94a3b8; background: #1a1a2e; border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 10px; }
  .done { color: #4CAF50; font-weight: 700; }
  .pend { color: #64748b; }
  .fq-mock-ai { width: 60px; margin: 0 auto; display: block; }
  .fq-mock-bubble { background: #1a1a2e; border-radius: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 2px; padding: 8px 10px; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.5; }
  .fq-mock-ex-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #94a3b8; padding: 4px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a3e; }

  .fq-badges { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 6px; }
  .fq-badge-item {
    background: #1a1a2e; border: 1px solid #2a2a3e;
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 4px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 3px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .fq-badge-item span { font-size: 0.55rem; color: #64748b; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; }
  .fq-badge-item.unlocked { border-color: rgba(255,215,0,0.3); background: rgba(255,215,0,0.05); }
  .fq-badge-item.unlocked span { color: #FFD700; }
  .fq-badge-item.locked { opacity: 0.35; filter: grayscale(1); }

  /* TECH */
  .fq-tech-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .fq-tech-item {
    background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
  }
  .fq-tech-item > span { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .fq-tech-item strong { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
